title: Pure Point Golf - Consistency Off the Tee - The Long Game
description:
Repost copy of Pure Point Golf with a fine young instructor Kyle Hallberg.
Kyle will give you the basics of consistent tee shots. You also will learn
how to cure some common tee faults - cure for slices, hooks, pushes, pulls,topped shots and sky balls.  This video will give you a simple system to be consistent
in your long game.  It is a must see for any weekend golfer.
